426
00:34:02,217 --> 00:34:04,115
Word quickly got out.

427
00:34:09,979 --> 00:34:12,966
- -
- You have 19 messages.

428
00:34:13,044 --> 00:34:15,530
Four job offers, my bank
raising my line of credit,

429
00:34:15,608 --> 00:34:17,267
